msgid "Episode I: Escape the Living"
msgstr "エピソード I: 生の逃走"

#. [campaign]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/_main.cfg:63
msgid ""
"This is the tale of an age when the glory of Wesnoth was transformed into "
"arrogance. The fugitive necromancer Gwiti Ha’atel is resolved to master the "
"undead hordes and exact his revenge against all who have betrayed him. His "
"journey soon leaves his own hands, morphing into an enormous wave of "
"power...\n"
"\n"
"(Intermediate level, 8 scenarios.)"
msgstr ""
"これは Wesnoth の栄光が傲慢へと姿を変えた時代の物語。逃走したネクロマンサー "
"Gwiti Ha’atel は、アンデッドの大軍団を支配し、彼を裏切った全ての人々へ復讐を"
"果たす事を決意した。彼の旅はやがて彼自身の手を離れ、巨大な力の波へと変貌を遂"
"げる......\n"
"\n"
"（中級レベル、8 シナリオ）"

