#. [campaign]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/_main.cfg:79
msgid "Episode II: The Death March"
msgstr "エピソード II: 死の行軍"

#. [campaign]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/_main.cfg:79
msgid ""
"At last, the deadly forces of Gwiti begin their invasion against Wesnoth. As "
"the shadows of his rule terrorize the Kingdom and its people, they turn to "
"the elven enchantress Elynia for their last hope. Will it be the Light or "
"the Darkness that stands in the end? No one who knows — except for only "
"one.\n"
"\n"
"(Intermediate level, 6 scenarios.)"
msgstr ""
"遂に Gwiti の死の力が Wesnoth に対する侵略を開始した。彼の支配する影が王国と"
"その人々を恐怖に陥れる中、彼らは最後の望みをエルフの魔法使い Elynia に託す。"
"最後に立っているのは光か、それとも闇なのか？知る者はただ一人を除いて存在しな"
"かった。\n"
"\n"
"（中級レベル、6 シナリオ）"

